The ptext package

A package similar to the lipsum package for the Persian language
with 100 paragraphs of the Shahnameh

Author: Vahid Damanafshan <vdamanafshan@kut.ac.ir>
Copyright (C) 2012-2013 by Vahid Damanafshan <http://www.damanafshan.ir>

============================================================
1. Contents of the package
--------------------------

   ptext.sty
   ptext.tex 
   ptext.pdf
   README   (this file)

To run the documentation, you must have the XB Niloofar and the Yas fonts on your computer.



